  "detailed_description": "《Memory Of Courage -勇气的记忆-》将通过九位不同职业角色的冒险故事，讲述一个关于勇气与记忆的故事。每个角色的冒险故事都有单独的主题，以及符合该职业对应的玩法。在某些重要的选择甚至会影响该冒险故事的走向和结局。无论你选择哪个职业开始，最终他们都将会汇聚在一起，共同拯救即将崩溃的世界！<br><br><br>进入游戏后，会有开始职业角色选择，每个职业都有不同的属性倾向，以及故事主题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/11a65056e6b310199d3e6de06772ae29.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/11a65056e6b310199d3e6de06772ae29.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/11a65056e6b310199d3e6de06772ae29.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>除了角色扮演游戏最基础的回合制战斗外，还有对应职业的谜题需要你来挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/89598c95d1c12db37ecdd58e5f270c3d.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/89598c95d1c12db37ecdd58e5f270c3d.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/89598c95d1c12db37ecdd58e5f270c3d.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/3c7227c157ddf3fc69d44185fa1f7dd6.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/3c7227c157ddf3fc69d44185fa1f7dd6.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/3c7227c157ddf3fc69d44185fa1f7dd6.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>你需要在故事进行中做出各种各样的抉择，每个选择都会导致故事朝着不同的方向进行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/410f1d7602221f0e29e0f37b01ae9b99.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/410f1d7602221f0e29e0f37b01ae9b99.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/410f1d7602221f0e29e0f37b01ae9b99.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>有的篇章里面甚至还有隐藏的结局，需要依靠你在游戏过程中仔细观察和推理，找到正确的道路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/23a65f3873462381a62ee76d33f610ec.avif?t=1706993129\" width=498 height=280 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/228c444554c7a0894dbd0fa8e065406e.avif?t=1706993129\" width=498 height=280 /></span><br><br><br><br>每个故事都有跌宕起伏的剧情，以及动画演出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/6103ce199df27495572f2af7dc0333ef.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/6103ce199df27495572f2af7dc0333ef.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/6103ce199df27495572f2af7dc0333ef.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>在最关键时候你还需要挑战强大的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/a203aede0b46e0239c3d9a83dcff8a84.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=558 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/a203aede0b46e0239c3d9a83dcff8a84.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/a203aede0b46e0239c3d9a83dcff8a84.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>当触发特殊事件的时候，还会有CG画面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/f52046b914f8be87ad1b57bb652d22db.poster.avif?t=1706993129\" width=532 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/f52046b914f8be87ad1b57bb652d22db.webm?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778300/extras/f52046b914f8be87ad1b57bb652d22db.mp4?t=1706993129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br>目前已经实装了以下职业的冒险故事：<br><br>佣兵         克雷德     <br>自然术士  楸      <br>学者         利瓦伊<br>樵夫         凯欧堤<br>铁匠         纳瑟夫<br><br>游戏将会持续更新下去，直到所有职业的故事讲述完毕。<br>希望能给你带来一次丰富精彩的大冒险之旅。<br><br><br>------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>常见问题解答：<br><strong>1. 目前游戏的状况？</strong><br>目前游戏已经完成九个角色之中五个角色的剧情故事。后续会继续更新完剩下的内容，请留意公告。如果介意请等待未来完整游戏开发完毕，谢谢您的关注！<br><br><strong>2. 目前的游戏价格和以后完整游戏价格有何差别？</strong><br>当前游戏价格为当前游戏内容的价格，后续更新后价格会有所不同。后续以整体更新为主，不会有DLC，也不会额外收费。<br><br><strong>3. 关于特殊剧情部分？</strong><br>该游戏为全年龄向。部分角色缺失CG剧情，会在以后更新后补充。请留意后续公告。<br><br><strong>4. 已通关的角色想再次挑战怎么办？</strong><br>由于涉及到过多的数据处理，暂时没办法实现该功能。<br><br><strong>5. 关于更新周期。</strong><br>如果没有特殊状况的话，更新周期大概会以2-3个月为周期进行更新。<br><br><strong>7.运行的Windows版本</strong><br>由于设备限制，目前只测试能在Windows10上运行，无法保证在Windows11，或者其他系统运行。如无法运行，请选择退款，十分抱歉。<br><br><strong>8.关于游戏。</strong><br>由于是第一次开发，难免会有很多不足的地方，请大家多多包涵。后续会根据反馈逐渐改善，谢谢您的支持。",
